headline.main: Funeral Held for Boy, 14, Found Drowned in Los Angeles River
headline.print_headline: Funeral Held for Boy, 14, Found Drowned in Los Angeles River

lead_paragraph: About 1,000 people have turned out to honor a 14-year-old boy who was found drowned in the Los Angeles River after a storm.
